race.comment: Plenty of chances in this. SCREAM (5) was good this trip two back then well off best latest. Has the inside gate here and the pace to use it. Should give a sight. REDEMPTION TIME (9) had been going very well including a win two back then was off best last time. Will wind up strongly and is worth another chance. FOX MAN (1) was a winner two back then weakened last time. Better draw and change of rider. Gets chance to atone.  THE WAYFARER (6) is on the quick back-up after finishing second over 1100m at Kerang on December 27. Long overdue and among the chances again.  SIMPLY LUSCIOUS (10) is well placed with the claim and rates strongly on best form.
